# Screenshot Manager App â€” Phase 1: Setup & Import

## Requirements
- Mac mini (M4 or later)
- Xcode 15+ (SwiftUI recommended)
- iOS Simulator or physical device (iOS 15+)

## Setup
1. Clone repo or `git init`
2. Open project in Xcode
3. Build & run on simulator/device

## Features (Phase 1)
- TabBar navigation (Home, Categories, Search, Settings)
- Request Photos permission
- List screenshots from Photos album
- Import metadata (id, date, thumbnail)
- Store in Core Data (Screenshot entity)
- Settings: toggle background import, clear cache

## Next Steps
Proceed to Phase 2: OCR & Categorization
